article.headline: Lamar 76, SE Louisiana 65
article.story: BEAUMONT, Texas -- Kenny Dawkins scored 24 points and Jay Brown scored 12 points and grabbed 12 rebounds to lead Lamar to a 76-65 victory over Southeastern Louisiana on Saturday night. Dawkins made four 3-pointers for the Cardinals (10-4, 1-0 Southland), who never trailed. Coy Custer added 11 points and Brandon McThay had 10. Kevyn Green led the Lions (6-8, 0-1) with 24 points and Warrell Span added 14.
